data.description:
"Welcome to this charming two-story historical home in Anoka, with a timeless appeal. With 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this residence offers a perfect blend of historic charm and modern comfort
The property features a unique 3-car garage, one stall equipped with a convenient workshop area. The spacious concrete driveway provides ample parking space.
Step into the large fenced backyard and discover your own oasis — complete with a Tiki bar for entertaining, a cozy firepit for gatherings, and a handy storage shed. This outdoor space is perfect for relaxing and hosting friends and family.
Enjoy the convenience of dual zoning, allowing for both business and residential use. The location is ideal — within walking distance to downtown Anoka, close to the highway for easy commuting, and near shopping for your everyda needs.
Don't miss the opportunity to call this historical gem your home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the unique charm of this Anoka residence!"
